org.springframework.boot.security

类 ApplicationContextRequestMatcher<C>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.boot.security.ApplicationContextRequestMatcher<C>
  • 类型参数:
    C - The type of the context that the match method actually needs to use. Can be an ApplicationContext, a class of an existing bean or a custom type that will be created on demand.
    所有已实现的接口:
    org.springframework.security.web.util.matcher.RequestMatcher
    直接已知子类:
    EndpointRequest.EndpointRequestMatcher, StaticResourceRequest.StaticResourceRequestMatcher

    public abstract class ApplicationContextRequestMatcher<C>
extends Object
implements org.springframework.security.web.util.matcher.RequestMatcher
    ApplicationContext backed RequestMatcher. Can work directly with the ApplicationContext, obtain an existing bean or create a new bean that is autowired in the usual way.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.0.0
    作者:
    Phillip Webb
